==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Plaquette
<hw>Pla`quette"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F., dim. of
<ets>plaque</ets> plate, plaque. See <er>Plaque</er>.]</ety> <def>A
small plaque, esp., in modern medal engraving, a small and delicate
bas-relief, whether cast or struck from a die, or of form other than
circular.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

